data.description: Welcome to 1/2 acre of peaceful living. NO HOA or Rear NEIGHBORS!! Plenty of room and parking for all of your toys. This 2 bedroom, 1 bath home is the perfect starter home, second home, rental income or if you just want a little privacy from the hustle and bustle of city living. Don't worry about upgrades as they have already been done. **NEW ROOF, HOT WATER HEATER, NEW CABINETS, NEW APPLIANCES, CERAMIC TILE, WATER SOFTNER, AND FRESHLY PAINTED**Not only is there a 1 car garage, there is a 1 car carport, and a parking pad in the back. Enjoy your morning coffee on your front screened in porch, or you can retreat to your large oversized screened back porch which is also perfect for entertaining. Fully equipped with a bar and pool table. Now just mount a TV for watching all of the football games. Just picture setting on your back porch and taking in the beautiful sightings of turkey's, and deer coming for a visit. You do not want to miss out on seeing this well maintained home that has so much to offer. Far enough out but close to everything. Schedule your showing before it is gone.
